{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "溺火", "storyInfo": "拉芙希妮得到“放逐王”的幫助，穿越了黑林的封鎖，與先前分開的友人們重逢。遺跡中，守靈人拒絕了拉芙希妮的未盡之言，但接受了為逝者舉辦葬禮的請求。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g8_blackforest_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……先前遇到的那個，難道又是捉弄人的幻影？路是錯的，我好像又走回來了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也看不清楚天色，不知道走了多久……還有多遠。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我沒像布莉吉說的那樣，被黑霧和噪音擋在黑林之外，至少我進來了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是這些愛捉弄人的精怪、會指錯路給你的幻影、故意牽來枝條絆倒人的羽獸……倒是和我帶莫蘭他們回來時差不多。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是這些樹木長得太高，也太茂密。它們遮住了天空，讓這裡面的生命與外界不同。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g9_blackforest_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒走錯路，這裡就是黑林的中心了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總感覺……這裡的景色也和我來的時候不一樣……那些代表秋天的金紅色呢？為什麼都消失了？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼裡面變成現在這樣？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是黑霧？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，黑林最終還是拒絕我了，是嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮緊緊握住手中的武器。假如真的如涅梅絲所說，深池離開城市之後就再也沒有回來，被黑霧吞噬的確是他們最有可能的下場。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但黑霧並無攻擊她的跡象，只是停在原地。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是在……拒絕我嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，與其說是拒絕，倒不如說是冷漠……失望？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了植物婆娑的晃動之外，沒有任何能被當成回答的聲響。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮搖搖頭，謹慎地經過黑霧身側，選擇了盡頭看起來有光亮的一條路，而黑霧仍然對她的通過無動於衷。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些樂於把人帶上歧途的精怪，此刻也不見蹤影。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g9_blackforest_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，又是死路……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒時間在這裡逗留了。抱歉，我得燒出一條路——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你真的是想太多了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得呢？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會是……你？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在城裡的那位……先生。上次我就有問題要問你，但你卻——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次見面確實算得上是不歡而散，不告而別。後面我也跟了你一路，看了你一路，就當是反思了。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我得承認你和我想的不太一樣，但現在還不是閒聊的時候。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別燒那些樹木，只用你的火照亮它們就行了，看看它們到底是什麼東西。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“是什麼東西”……？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葉片鋒利，荊棘堅硬，枝條上甚至反射出金屬的冷光？這究竟是？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼不重要，你的火不可能燒掉這些東西，這才是重點。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我來。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在黑霧改變主意之前，跟我來！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#6$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再晚一點跟你搭話，那個東西的心情稍微變差，你就會被直接吞了，骨頭屑也不剩。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那邊不是死路嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼覺得眼見的東西就一定為實呢？", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽我的，走！", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g7_blackforest_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……我來納斯爾紗時走的那條路！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那些小路竟然通向這裡？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，雖然冒昧，但您和林中的精怪……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別傻了，我怎麼會和它們扯上關係。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是這片樹林，幾百年過去了，除了多了一層黑霧以外，裡面竟然還是這副樣子……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，煞風景。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再往前幾步就算是離開黑林了，不知道您能否——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖嘖，這還真是……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生什麼事了？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你身後。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草！", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，我們來了！", "name": "塔拉流民"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "流民們的身影出現在黑林明亮的邊緣。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡是不是出了什麼事？自從你進城之後，黑霧就像是突然發怒了一樣，將城市和外界嚴密地隔開，黑林這邊已經好幾天沒有人出入了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才有人去黑林外圍打獵，聽見林中有響動，有人聲，還有火光什麼的。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前也出過類似的事，守靈人讓我們不要靠近黑林，小心惹禍上身。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這一次我們都認出來了，那是你的火。我們必須得過來。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡太危險了——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不該放任你一個人去承擔所有的危險。倫蒂尼姆郊外那次，我們在沼澤地等你的時候，大家就已經明白了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們信任你，你也該信任我們。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很感激。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不算什麼。我們先回聚落吧。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，不知道您——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，怎麼了？你在對誰說話？還有人跟著你從黑林裡出來嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍轉身看去，那個不請自來的男人就像是陽光下的露珠一樣不見蹤影。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你們為這些人提供了住所，守靈人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲將他們託付給我們，這就是我們應該做的。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，拉芙希妮小姐，守靈人承諾不將您的存在洩露給任何不知情的人。既然您已經確認了這些人的安危，我們可以就此分開了。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼意思？難道你們不歡迎她？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭，你們也一樣。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩條紅龍之間總會產生無盡的紛爭。如果你們擅自介入兩條紅龍之間的爭鬥，那我們也無力再為你們提供庇護。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們怎麼這樣？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一向如此。守靈人既不挑起衝突，也不試圖消弭衝突。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生者的爭端非我們所能干涉，我們只守望逝者的靈魂。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍，如果您真的如莫蘭等人所說，是一位悲憫而高尚的領導者，那您就更不該將這些無辜的人捲入您的鬥爭。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是兩條紅龍之間的爭鬥，我是為了納斯爾紗的居民來向你們求助——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬥爭總有理由。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草不是一個會找藉口的人。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#5$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便不是藉口，生者的糾紛也與我們無關……這是我們至今仍在為之品嚐苦果的教訓。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請回吧。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我來請你們安葬一位逝者……也不行嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安葬逝者？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果的確如此，守靈人的營地會向您敞開，但也僅限葬禮。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩請告訴我逝者的姓名、事蹟，還有……請把他的亡骸交給我們。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他叫……庫林，城裡的鐵匠。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林？！", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的死因是什麼？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他被紫色的死火奪取了生命與意志，即便是我的火焰……也無法再拯救他。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼從所謂獨立到現在，沒有一個納斯爾紗人來找我們，讓我們幫城內的逝者舉行一場符合傳統的葬禮呢？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來……", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭結束後，第一個得到哀悼的納斯爾紗人……甚至沒有死在那場戰爭中。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像這樣……把乾草紮成環？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，然後把這些花卉裝飾在上面，編成花環就行了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得我們在路上也有這麼一次，農民們把花環戴在你的頭上，祈求來年風調雨順。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真懷念啊，感覺又回到那個時候了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡住得不開心？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自己倒是很自在，但其他人可能多少會覺得有些拘束吧。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為守靈人的生活就像在和自己過不去嘛。莫蘭，你那個詞是怎麼說的？“苦修”？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不喝酒，不開宴會，不吃過分烹飪的東西，甚至不會大聲說笑。每天從天不亮起床開始，直到半夜睡下，無論做什麼都有儀式。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然他們不用這一套來要求我們，但我們畢竟也得幫人家做些農活什麼的，還是要打交道的。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天住下來，我都覺得自己快要不會笑了，哈哈。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有莫蘭每天都會去找守靈人說話，每天都能學一點東西回來。今天是繩結的編法，明天是如何估算樹木壽命之類的。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒是沒錯，不過和那些故事中的守靈人相比……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍閣下？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守靈人女士。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到您會在這裡與他們一同勞作。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草一直都是這樣啊。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要我們迴避嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是為了儀式需要，來確認死者的生平。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請告訴我，紅龍，這段時間裡，庫林身上究竟發生什麼事情了？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會一五一十地把我見到的一切告訴你，守靈人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望這些事能對你有所觸動。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}